business?

::Neody/Havoc/Repressor::

Neody nods and climbs into Falcon, wondering what flying was like.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
"Ok. Contact Zardus if you need assistance," Havoc says and turns 
around.

"Lets go," he says to the other Warmachines, transforming into jet 
mode and flying off. Repressor trasnforms and follows.
